Question:
https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/the-pads/

SQL QUERY:
SELECT
    Name || '(' || SUBSTR(Occupation,1,1) || ')'
FROM OCCUPATIONS
ORDER BY 1;
 
SELECT
    'There are a total of ' || COUNT(Name) || ' ' || LOWER(Occupation)
    || 's.'
FROM OCCUPATIONS
GROUP BY Occupation
ORDER BY COUNT(Name), Occupation;


